## ~/src/cpp/lib/com/OS/.README
##############################################################################

This subdirectory contains subdirectories for platform dependent code.

Platform specific files are not meant to be compiled directly, but are
only included when appropriate.  The platform specific include file is
selected using the following platform and operating system controls.
These controls are set by platform-specific Makefiles.

Operating systems:
------------------
_OS_BSD         Unix or unix derivitive
_OS_WIN         Microsoft Windows


_OS             Platform       Associated
Directive       Directive      Varient
---------       ---------      ------------
_OS_BSD         _OS_CYGWIN     Cygnus BSD on Windows
_OS_BSD         _OS_LINUX      Linux Unix
_OS_BSD         _OS_UNIX       Generic Unix
_OS_WIN         _OS_WIN        Microsoft Windows


                Nominal
SubDirectory    Platform
------------    --------
BSD             BSD (Unix)
WIN             Microsoft Windows
